<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="Aink343">
<l>avarō vārār tāṉvan taṉṟē</l>
<l>tiṇinilaik kōṅkam payanta</l>
<l>aṇimiku koḻumukai yuṭaiyum poḻutē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l>Won’t he himself come? The season has arrived,</l>
<l>when thick buds of great beauty, </l>
<l>yielded by the firm Myrobalan trees, break open. </l>
      </lg>
    </div>
